<br>
Erolis Bloodthorn = Familiar of life<br>
Grants a 20% bonus to health regeneration. Wizard and/or group.<br>
<br>
Most importantly the benefit of calling forth a familiar should be equally dangerous if you accidently loose your precious friend to a frenzied mob.<br>
<br>
Let the familiars have from 100 to 1000 HPs dependant on the lvl of the wizard, and make the wizard take a system shock damage equal to the total damage done to the pet.  I'm sure, even at lvl 60, you wouldn't want to loose you familiar and recieve a system shock hit for 1000 pts of damage.<br>
<br>
Keep the ideas comming.  Once Verant opens up for the wizard class discussion we should present him with a full list of current fixes and a wishlist for additions including this familiar thread =)<br>
